Class ObjectResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emc.esu.api.ObjectResult

  • public class ObjectResult
extends java.lang.Object
    ObjectResults are returned from listObjectsWithMetadata. They contain the object's ID as well as its MetadataList.
